{"tid":1564531,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[光復香港 時代革命] 黃雨衣","createTime":"2019-09-12T22:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T22:12:10.000Z","uid":42860,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3c049e30c913da8e1001a8bb51a4b605165935b0","tid":1564531,"uid":42860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:00:19.000Z","msg":"適逢中秋佳節<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但革命尚未成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又見有人整左個黃頭盔燈籠(冇圖)<br />\n小弟不才，但又想整啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就用左兩粒鐘趕住係中秋前整到<br />\n就整左以下件黃雨衣燈飾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都知做得唔太好<br />\n要屌就屌細力啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6yjarH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6yjarH.png&h=41e62683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\n祈求民主 與自由 萬世都 不 朽<br />\n我願榮 光歸 香港"},{"pid":"de13fd47385c83a5ebdab22995bd3a9e7ed9fe6c","tid":1564531,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T22:01:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"08b060ad29492aa7b561ddbc